Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:28.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…永遠普遍の愛なんて　信じられるのかしら？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:34.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甘い紅茶に溶かす　ため息模様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:39.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう　待ちくたびれたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:47.91,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを追いかけて　堕ちるワンダーランド
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.29,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまで行けばいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}イロトリドリの闇を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:23:02.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}道標の旋律　心が騒ぎだす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:06.19,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時計仕掛けの運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}壊してしまえ　私は自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:13.26,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが真実
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:21.07,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze　生きる証
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:28.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…是否能相信  所謂永恆的愛？…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:34.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘆息溶化於甘美紅茶  化為波紋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.30,0:22:39.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已經  再也按捺不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:47.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追尋著你  墜落往  Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何處才是盡頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}穿越色彩斑斕的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:23:02.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指明前路的旋律  踴動不已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:06.19,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}假使命運如時鐘般不可逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:09.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}破壞它  我將獲得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:13.26,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你是唯一的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:21.07,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}Catcher in a Maze  是我生存的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？很懷念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…全都記得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…真的是基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:55.53,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自深淵的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在這裡也許還比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是由我來保護主人的  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會背叛您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬扯斷了多魯達姆的線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜  今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情節發展和我寫的劇本不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請期待下次的舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲·貝薩流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣息完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是真的逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…啊…艾莉絲  你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有受傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來沒有呢  呵…呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想死嗎你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會想死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…萬一我沒停手的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有那覺悟了  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你絕對會停手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是基爾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「絕對」會停手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…才不相信什麼「絕對」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我想那種東西相信一次也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會背叛您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕對不會讓別人傷害到您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你所說的「絕對」  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是你所認識的那個基爾巴特了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是基爾巴特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特…雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與貝薩流斯家互不兩立的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四大公爵家之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特雷家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不要再像從前那樣對我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那個資格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  那傢伙在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈特雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  那根本不能算什麼解釋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙對我來說  是比誰都重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都有機會告訴他事實的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道總有一天會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我卻一直沒能開口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  真是不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還有別的敵人  要快點回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡都過了十年了  還是一點都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你問我做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來幫你包紮傷口的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  把圍巾給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你  還有愛達三個人  在這房子探險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探險途中掉進這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺…哇哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你沒事吧  基爾巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…真是令人懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對我來說  這是最近才發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  一直瞞著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有所改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不想被你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…果然…真像是你會做的事  真遜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你變了…哪裡變了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是變得比我高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是變得會開槍了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都過了十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有些變化也是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對我來說  就算有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是以前的那個你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我醒來時  你總是最先出現在我身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有剛才  你也守護了「絕對」的諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說  你到底哪裡變得不像以前的你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算是現在  也還相信著那時的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼  我都會陪在您身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後就算時光流逝  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算兩人的立場有了變化…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成了公爵家的人  那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  貝薩流斯家和奈特雷家的關係很惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不過是成了個貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我會放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…你還是和從前一樣蠻橫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可是背叛了貝薩流斯家的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也願意原諒我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦  如果你希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想永遠做您的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在仍然願意做您的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了  基爾巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  和我說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人  不要和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你應該明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你跑到哪裡  到最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤伶伶的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你是艾莉絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你…是艾莉絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該是…染血黑兔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧  臉色很差啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉他怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我讓他在墓碑前等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們原本就是來調查那個墓碑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  艾莉絲也要一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…該不會是因為丟下你一個人而生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那一腳…是不是太狠了點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴你這人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然丟下我一個人跑掉是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你  害我做了個噁心的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶我過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒和那傢伙談過  這裡的詳細情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  艾莉絲對這裡的事  也不太瞭解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起聽的話  說不定你能想起些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想整理一下思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能從阿比斯逃出來  我是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾也…還陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還有很多事讓我覺得沒有真實感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾  怎麼樣了  有沒有發現什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  如果能知道這是誰的墓就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣啦  艾莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聲音太微弱了  剛才都沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樹…這花瓣裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點的寄宿著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等待著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是…笨兔子的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰…在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不聽話的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟在我後面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在艾莉絲的記憶中出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你正被「阿比斯的意志」監視著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶的空間  開始崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可要好好守護他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿比斯的意志」到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透不過氣了  基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情報我也不清楚  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是創造出現在的阿比斯的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是潘多拉和巴斯卡維爾一直以來追求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是  那隻兔子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那恐怕只是個替身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…終於見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在等你哦  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  我準備了好多人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來玩人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起聊天  聊到想睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  還有  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來吧  我心愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不認識你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…能不能放了艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是靈體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是總有一天會毀滅你的存在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要插手我和他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…明明對那孩子一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還想陪在她身邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…和艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  那種連自己是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己出生在這世上的理由都不明白的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她…卻奪走了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒生下來該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒生下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩掉那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實正如你所說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對艾莉絲一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得不能丟下她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得她和我有相似之處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會和艾莉絲在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何根據
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是  相信我的感覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  雖然有點可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你沒什麼好談的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得你這麼盛情邀請我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很不巧  現在的我比起玩人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更喜歡去尋寶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔沒選我  而選擇了黑兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到阿比斯的意志居然這麼早就出來干涉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  其它都和我們預料的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧  回到潘多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}解開所有謎團  獲知真相的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}奧茲同學是「那樣的」存在哦
